As their lips met, she didn't stay a stranger to it. Leaning into him, her 
form against his, one arm over his shoulder the other under his arm & over his 
back... she returned the kiss with wild passion to show how much she indeed 
cared for him & also how much he would do anything for him & the Decepticon 
cause.
